title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best Of The Dan Patrick Show
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP talks to SEC Commissioner Greg Sankey about his 5 year plan for the conference. Chris Mannix calls in to discuss KD giving Nets ownership an ultimatum. And ESPN's Sal Paolantonio discusses the process of Pro Football HOF voting.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
